_______________________________________________________________________________
"Inflict Pain"    
        This allows the psionicist to generate artificial feelings of
        pain in the target.  It does no actual damage, but the target
        will act as if his str and dex were much lower due to the intense
        crippling effects of the power.  It has a variable duration based
        on guild level.
 
SP Cost:  40		Guild Level:  9	Potential Points:  3
 
Command:  inflict <target>
